description: Provides normalization of Certificate Authority ingested data.

calculations.expression: case(Public_Key_Algorithm=="RSA" AND Hash_Algorithm_Size>= 256 AND Public_Key_Size >= 2048, "Recommended", Public_Key_Algorithm=="ECC" AND Hash_Algorithm_Size >= 384 AND Encoded_Key_Parameters=="06 05 2B 81 04 00 22", "Recommended", Public_Key_Algorithm=="ECC" AND Hash_Algorithm_Size>= 256 AND Encoded_Key_Parameters=="06 08 2A 86 48 CE 3D 03 01 07", "Recommended", Public_Key_Algorithm=="ECC" AND isnull(Encoded_Key_Parameters), "Unknown", 1=1, "Not Recommended")

case(Whitelist_Status = "TRUE" AND Blacklist_Status = "TRUE", "Appears in Whitelist and Blacklist", Whitelist_Status = "TRUE", "White", Blacklist_Status = "TRUE", "Black", isnull(Whitelist_Status) AND isnull(Blacklist_Status), "Gray")
